al-development#ref68659">Expansion of Buddhism</a></li></ul><ul class="list-unstyled" data-level="h3"><li data-target="#ref68660"><a href="/topic/Buddhism/Historical-development#ref68660">Buddhism under the Guptas and Palas</a></li></ul><ul class="list-unstyled" data-level="h3"><li data-target="#ref68661"><a href="/topic/Buddhism/The-demise-of-Buddhism-in-India">The demise of Buddhism in India</a></li></ul><ul class="list-unstyled" data-level="h3"><li data-target="#ref68662"><a href="/topic/Buddhism/The-demise-of-Buddhism-in-India#ref68662">Contemporary revival</a></li></ul></li></ul><ul class="list-unstyled" data-level="h2"><li data-target="#ref68663"><a href="/topic/Buddhism/The-demise-of-Buddhism-in-India#ref68663">Sri Lanka and Southeast Asia</a><ul class="list-unstyled" data-level="h3"><li data-target="#ref68664"><a href="/topic/Buddhism/The-demise-of-Buddhism-in-India#ref68664">Sri Lanka</a></li></ul><ul class="list-unstyled" data-level="h3"><li data-target="#ref68665" class="has-children"><a href="/topic/Buddhism/Southeast-Asia">Southeast Asia</a><ul class="list-unstyled" data-level="h4"><li data-target="#ref68666"><a href="/topic/Buddhism/Southeast-Asia#ref68666">Malaysia and Indonesia</a></li></ul><ul class="list-unstyled" data-level="h4"><li data-target="#ref68667"><a href="/topic/Buddhism/Southeast-Asia#ref68667">From Myanmar to the Mekong delta</a></li></ul><ul class="list-unstyled" data-level="h4"><li data-target="#ref68668"><a href="/topic/Buddhism/Southeast-Asia#ref68668">Vietnam</a></li></ul></li></ul></li></ul><ul class="list-unstyled" data-level="h2"><li data-target="#ref68669"><a href="/topic/Buddhism/Central-Asia-and-China">Central Asia and China</a><ul class="list-unstyled" data-level="h3"><li data-target="#ref68670"><a href="/topic/Buddhism/Central-Asia-and-China#ref68670">Central Asia</a></li></ul><ul class="list-unstyled" data-level="h3"><li data-target="#ref68671" class="has-children"><a href="/topic/Buddhism/Central-Asia-and-China#ref68671"